    | N1 | <&check> |
    | N2 | <&check> |
    | N3 | <&check> |
    | N4 | - |
    | N5 | - |
end note

note top of N5
    |= Node |= P |
    | N1 | <&check> |
    | N2 | - |
    | N3 | - |
    | N4 | - |
    | N5 | <&check> |
end note

note top of N4
    |= Node |= P |
    | N1 | <&check> |
    | N2 | <&check> |
    | N3 | <&check> |
    | N4 | <&check> |
    | N5 | <&check> |
end note

@enduml